<br>
I could carry on in Feerrott or Eastern Wastes, but ulthorks and spectres are blue, though ... seems a waste when I can handle yellows if they don't have too many HP.  I'm wondering where I should be looking to hunt next.  I would be soloing, so crowd control is an issue.<br>
<br>
In the enchanter thread there was mention of Ulthork man o' wars near Kael?  Or giants in Firiona Vie - but would I be KOS there?  I considered the pyramids in Dreadlands, but the skeletons have a lot of HP and some are still red to me.  I know Scarlet Desert is supposed to be good for magicians, but am I old enough yet?  My experience being a SK doesn't really help, since the fighting styles are very different and the SK was much weaker.  So I'd be interested in tips on the best places to be soloing most efficiently... any thoughts on where to find low-40s mobs with few HPs? <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><br>
